                            <li>To analyze and recognize existing result-oriented pedagogical practices </li>
                            <li>To develop innovative and effective pedagogical practices  </li>
                            <li>To pilot these effective pedagogical practices in selected institutions to evaluate their efficacy in enhancing learning outcomes </li>
                            <li>To generate evidence-based models of pedagogical practices </li>
                            <li>To utilize successful evidence-based models of pedagogical practices for capacity-building of educators and institutions</li>
                            <li>To disseminate and showcase successful and evidence-based of pedagogical models to stakeholders and communities for purposeful engazement </li>
